This project is a Linux-based file integrity Monitoring(FIM) system built on ubuntu that monitors critical system directoriess and detects unautharized changes in real time.

The tool watches sensitive files and generates alerts when 

- Files are modified
-Permissions change
-Ownership changes
-Files are created

This Project simulates a host-based intrusion detection system (HIDS) Similar to enterprise tools like tripwire or OSSEC
